{
  "video_id": "nAMrtHC2Ev0",
  "title": "Rachel Armstrong: Architecture that repairs itself?",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 15260.0,
      "end_time": 19259.0,
      "text": "All buildings today have something in common."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 19260.0,
      "end_time": 22260.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re made using Victorian technologies."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 22260.0,
      "end_time": 25260.0,
      "text": "This involves blueprints,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 25260.0,
      "end_time": 27260.0,
      "text": "industrial manufacturing"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 27260.0,
      "end_time": 30260.0,
      "text": "and construction using teams of workers."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 30260.0,
      "end_time": 33260.0,
      "text": "All of this effort results in an inert object."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 33260.0,
      "end_time": 36260.0,
      "text": "And that means that there is a one-way transfer of energy"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 36260.0,
      "end_time": 40260.0,
      "text": "from our environment into our homes and cities."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 40260.0,
      "end_time": 42260.0,
      "text": "This is not sustainable."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 42260.0,
      "end_time": 45260.0,
      "text": "I believe that the only way that it is possible for us"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 45260.0,
      "end_time": 48260.0,
      "text": "to construct genuinely sustainable homes and cities"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 48260.0,
      "end_time": 50260.0,
      "text": "is by connecting them to nature,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 50260.0,
      "end_time": 53260.0,
      "text": "not insulating them from it."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 53260.0,
      "end_time": 57260.0,
      "text": "Now, in order to do this, we need the right kind of language."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 57260.0,
      "end_time": 59260.0,
      "text": "Living systems are in constant conversation"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 59260.0,
      "end_time": 61260.0,
      "text": "with the natural world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 61260.0,
      "end_time": 65259.0,
      "text": "through sets of chemical reactions called metabolism."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 65260.00000000001,
      "end_time": 68260.0,
      "text": "And this is the conversion of one group of substances"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 68260.0,
      "end_time": 70260.0,
      "text": "into another, either through"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 70260.0,
      "end_time": 73260.0,
      "text": "the production or the absorption of energy."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 73260.0,
      "end_time": 75260.0,
      "text": "And this is the way in which living materials"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 75260.0,
      "end_time": 78260.0,
      "text": "make the most of their local resources"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 78260.0,
      "end_time": 81260.0,
      "text": "in a sustainable way."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 81260.0,
      "end_time": 83260.0,
      "text": "So, I&#39;m interested in the use of"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 83260.0,
      "end_time": 88260.0,
      "text": "metabolic materials for the practice of architecture."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 88260.0,
      "end_time": 90260.0,
      "text": "But they don&#39;t exist. So I&#39;m having to make them."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 90260.0,
      "end_time": 92260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m working with architect Neil Spiller"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 92260.0,
      "end_time": 94260.0,
      "text": "at the Bartlett School of Architecture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 94260.0,
      "end_time": 96260.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;re collaborating with international scientists"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 96260.0,
      "end_time": 98260.0,
      "text": "in order to generate these new materials"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 98260.0,
      "end_time": 100260.0,
      "text": "from a bottom up approach."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 100260.0,
      "end_time": 102260.0,
      "text": "That means we&#39;re generating them from scratch."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 102260.0,
      "end_time": 106260.0,
      "text": "One of our collaborators is chemist Martin Hanczyc,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 106260.0,
      "end_time": 109260.0,
      "text": "and he&#39;s really interested in the transition from"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 109260.0,
      "end_time": 111260.0,
      "text": "inert to living matter."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 111260.0,
      "end_time": 114260.0,
      "text": "Now, that&#39;s exactly the kind of process that I&#39;m interested in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 114260.0,
      "end_time": 116260.0,
      "text": "when we&#39;re thinking about sustainable materials."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 116260.0,
      "end_time": 121260.0,
      "text": "So, Martin, he works with a system called the protocell."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 121260.0,
      "end_time": 124260.0,
      "text": "Now all this is -- and it&#39;s magic --"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 124260.0,
      "end_time": 127260.0,
      "text": "is a little fatty bag. And it&#39;s got a chemical battery in it."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 127260.0,
      "end_time": 130259.0,
      "text": "And it has no DNA."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 130258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 132260.0,
      "text": "This little bag is able to conduct itself"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 132260.0,
      "end_time": 135260.0,
      "text": "in a way that can only be described as living."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 135260.0,
      "end_time": 138260.0,
      "text": "It is able to move around its environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 138260.0,
      "end_time": 140260.0,
      "text": "It can follow chemical gradients."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 140260.0,
      "end_time": 143260.0,
      "text": "It can undergo complex reactions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 143260.0,
      "end_time": 147260.0,
      "text": "some of which are happily architectural."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 147260.0,
      "end_time": 149260.0,
      "text": "So here we are. These are protocells,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 149260.0,
      "end_time": 151260.0,
      "text": "patterning their environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 151260.0,
      "end_time": 154260.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t know how they do that yet."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 154260.0,
      "end_time": 158260.0,
      "text": "Here, this is a protocell, and it&#39;s vigorously shedding this skin."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 158260.0,
      "end_time": 160260.0,
      "text": "Now, this looks like a chemical kind of birth."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 160260.0,
      "end_time": 163260.0,
      "text": "This is a violent process."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 163260.0,
      "end_time": 166260.0,
      "text": "Here, we&#39;ve got a protocell to extract carbon dioxide"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 166260.0,
      "end_time": 168260.0,
      "text": "out of the atmosphere"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 168260.0,
      "end_time": 170260.0,
      "text": "and turn it into carbonate."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 170260.0,
      "end_time": 172260.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s the shell around that globular fat."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 172260.0,
      "end_time": 175260.0,
      "text": "They are quite brittle. So you&#39;ve only got a part of one there."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 175260.0,
      "end_time": 178260.0,
      "text": "So what we&#39;re trying to do is, we&#39;re trying to push these technologies"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 178260.0,
      "end_time": 180260.0,
      "text": "towards creating bottom-up construction approaches"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 180260.0,
      "end_time": 182260.0,
      "text": "for architecture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 182260.0,
      "end_time": 185260.0,
      "text": "which contrast the current, Victorian, top-down methods"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 185260.0,
      "end_time": 188260.0,
      "text": "which impose structure upon matter."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 188260.0,
      "end_time": 191260.0,
      "text": "That can&#39;t be energetically sensible."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 191260.0,
      "end_time": 193260.0,
      "text": "So, bottom-up materials"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 193260.0,
      "end_time": 195260.0,
      "text": "actually exist today."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 195260.0,
      "end_time": 198260.0,
      "text": "They&#39;ve been in use, in architecture, since ancient times."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 198260.0,
      "end_time": 201260.0,
      "text": "If you walk around the city of Oxford, where we are today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 201260.0,
      "end_time": 203260.0,
      "text": "and have a look at the brickwork,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 203260.0,
      "end_time": 205260.0,
      "text": "which I&#39;ve enjoyed doing in the last couple of days,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 205260.0,
      "end_time": 207260.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ll actually see that a lot of it is made of limestone."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 207260.0,
      "end_time": 209260.0,
      "text": "And if you look even closer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 209260.0,
      "end_time": 211260.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ll see, in that limestone, there are little shells"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 211260.0,
      "end_time": 214260.0,
      "text": "and little skeletons that are piled upon each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 214260.0,
      "end_time": 217260.0,
      "text": "And then they are fossilized over millions of years."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 217260.0,
      "end_time": 219260.0,
      "text": "Now a block of limestone, in itself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 219260.0,
      "end_time": 222260.0,
      "text": "isn&#39;t particularly that interesting."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 222260.0,
      "end_time": 224260.0,
      "text": "It looks beautiful."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 224260.0,
      "end_time": 228260.0,
      "text": "But imagine what the properties of this limestone block might be"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 228260.0,
      "end_time": 230260.0,
      "text": "if the surfaces were actually"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 230260.0,
      "end_time": 233260.0,
      "text": "in conversation with the atmosphere."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 233260.0,
      "end_time": 236260.0,
      "text": "Maybe they could extract carbon dioxide."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 236260.0,
      "end_time": 239260.0,
      "text": "Would it give this block of limestone new properties?"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 239260.0,
      "end_time": 242260.0,
      "text": "Well, most likely it would. It might be able to grow."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 242260.0,
      "end_time": 244260.0,
      "text": "It might be able to self-repair, and even respond"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 244260.0,
      "end_time": 246260.0,
      "text": "to dramatic changes"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 246260.0,
      "end_time": 248260.0,
      "text": "in the immediate environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 248260.0,
      "end_time": 251260.0,
      "text": "So, architects are never happy"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 251260.0,
      "end_time": 254260.0,
      "text": "with just one block of an interesting material."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 254260.0,
      "end_time": 256260.0,
      "text": "They think big. Okay?"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 256260.0,
      "end_time": 259260.0,
      "text": "So when we think about scaling up metabolic materials,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 259260.0,
      "end_time": 261260.0,
      "text": "we can start thinking about ecological interventions"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 261260.0,
      "end_time": 263260.0,
      "text": "like repair of atolls,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 263260.0,
      "end_time": 266260.0,
      "text": "or reclamation of parts of a city"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 266260.0,
      "end_time": 268260.0,
      "text": "that are damaged by water."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 268260.0,
      "end_time": 270260.0,
      "text": "So, one of these examples"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 270260.0,
      "end_time": 273260.0,
      "text": "would of course be the historic city of Venice."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 273260.0,
      "end_time": 277260.0,
      "text": "Now, Venice, as you know, has a tempestuous relationship with the sea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 277260.0,
      "end_time": 279260.0,
      "text": "and is built upon wooden piles."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 279260.0,
      "end_time": 282260.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;ve devised a way by which it may be possible"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 282260.0,
      "end_time": 284260.0,
      "text": "for the protocell technology that we&#39;re working with"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 284260.0,
      "end_time": 287260.0,
      "text": "to sustainably reclaim Venice."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 287260.0,
      "end_time": 289260.0,
      "text": "And architect Christian Kerrigan"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 289260.0,
      "end_time": 291260.0,
      "text": "has come up with a series of designs that show us"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 291260.0,
      "end_time": 294260.0,
      "text": "how it may be possible to actually grow a limestone reef"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 294260.0,
      "end_time": 296260.0,
      "text": "underneath the city."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 296260.0,
      "end_time": 299260.0,
      "text": "So, here is the technology we have today."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 299260.0,
      "end_time": 301260.0,
      "text": "This is our protocell technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 301260.0,
      "end_time": 305260.0,
      "text": "effectively making a shell, like its limestone forefathers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 305260.0,
      "end_time": 308260.0,
      "text": "and depositing it in a very complex environment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 308260.0,
      "end_time": 310260.0,
      "text": "against natural materials."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 310260.0,
      "end_time": 313260.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re looking at crystal lattices to see the bonding process in this."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 313260.0,
      "end_time": 315260.0,
      "text": "Now, this is the very interesting part."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 315260.0,
      "end_time": 318260.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t just want limestone dumped everywhere in all the pretty canals."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 318260.0,
      "end_time": 320260.0,
      "text": "What we need it to do is to be"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 320260.0,
      "end_time": 324260.0,
      "text": "creatively crafted around the wooden piles."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 324260.0,
      "end_time": 326260.0,
      "text": "So, you can see from these diagrams that the protocell is actually"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 326260.0,
      "end_time": 328260.0,
      "text": "moving away from the light,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 328260.0,
      "end_time": 330260.0,
      "text": "toward the dark foundations."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 330260.0,
      "end_time": 332260.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve observed this in the laboratory."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 332260.0,
      "end_time": 335260.0,
      "text": "The protocells can actually move away from the light."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 335260.0,
      "end_time": 338260.0,
      "text": "They can actually also move towards the light. You have to just choose your species."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 338260.0,
      "end_time": 340260.0,
      "text": "So that these don&#39;t just exist as one entity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 340260.0,
      "end_time": 343260.0,
      "text": "we kind of chemically engineer them."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 343260.0,
      "end_time": 346260.0,
      "text": "And so here the protocells are depositing their limestone"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 346260.0,
      "end_time": 349260.0,
      "text": "very specifically, around the foundations of Venice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 349260.0,
      "end_time": 351260.0,
      "text": "effectively petrifying it."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 351260.0,
      "end_time": 355260.0,
      "text": "Now, this isn&#39;t going to happen tomorrow. It&#39;s going to take a while."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 355260.0,
      "end_time": 359260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s going to take years of tuning and monitoring this technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 359260.0,
      "end_time": 361260.0,
      "text": "in order for us to become ready"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 361260.0,
      "end_time": 363260.0,
      "text": "to test it out in a case-by-case basis"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 363260.0,
      "end_time": 366260.0,
      "text": "on the most damaged and stressed buildings within the city of Venice."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 366260.0,
      "end_time": 369260.0,
      "text": "But gradually, as the buildings are repaired,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 369260.0,
      "end_time": 372260.0,
      "text": "we will see the accretion of a limestone reef beneath the city."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 372260.0,
      "end_time": 376260.0,
      "text": "An accretion itself is a huge sink of carbon dioxide."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 376260.0,
      "end_time": 379260.0,
      "text": "Also it will attract the local marine ecology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 379260.0,
      "end_time": 383260.0,
      "text": "who will find their own ecological niches within this architecture."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 383260.0,
      "end_time": 386260.0,
      "text": "So, this is really interesting. Now we have an architecture"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 386260.0,
      "end_time": 389260.0,
      "text": "that connects a city to the natural world"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 389260.0,
      "end_time": 391260.0,
      "text": "in a very direct and immediate way."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 391260.0,
      "end_time": 394260.0,
      "text": "But perhaps the most exciting thing about it"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 394260.0,
      "end_time": 397260.0,
      "text": "is that the driver of this technology is available everywhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 397260.0,
      "end_time": 400260.0,
      "text": "This is terrestrial chemistry. We&#39;ve all got it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 400260.0,
      "end_time": 403260.0,
      "text": "which means that this technology is just as appropriate"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 403260.0,
      "end_time": 405260.0,
      "text": "for developing countries as it is"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 405260.0,
      "end_time": 407260.0,
      "text": "for First World countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 407260.0,
      "end_time": 410260.0,
      "text": "So, in summary, I&#39;m generating metabolic materials"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 410260.0,
      "end_time": 413260.0,
      "text": "as a counterpoise to Victorian technologies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 413260.0,
      "end_time": 416260.0,
      "text": "and building architectures from a bottom-up approach."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 416260.0,
      "end_time": 418260.0,
      "text": "Secondly, these metabolic materials"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 418260.0,
      "end_time": 420260.0,
      "text": "have some of the properties of living systems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 420260.0,
      "end_time": 423260.0,
      "text": "which means they can perform in similar ways."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 423260.0,
      "end_time": 426260.0,
      "text": "They can expect to have a lot of forms and functions"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 426260.0,
      "end_time": 428260.0,
      "text": "within the practice of architecture."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 428260.0,
      "end_time": 431260.0,
      "text": "And finally, an observer in the future"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 431260.0,
      "end_time": 434260.0,
      "text": "marveling at a beautiful structure in the environment"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 434260.0,
      "end_time": 437260.0,
      "text": "may find it almost impossible to tell"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 437260.0,
      "end_time": 439260.0,
      "text": "whether this structure"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 439260.0,
      "end_time": 441260.0,
      "text": "has been created by a natural process"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 441260.0,
      "end_time": 443260.0,
      "text": "or an artificial one."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 443260.0,
      "end_time": 445260.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 445260.0,
      "end_time": 449260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}